p%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fmerman-sound%252Fid369670877%253Fi%253D369670884%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTISTNAME" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Glow In the Dark Safari Set-ISAN']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/autumn-never-fall.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/sunwrae.jpg" alt="Autumn Never Fall / Sunwrae" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/autumn-never-fall.php">Autumn Never Fall<br />Sunwrae</a></h4><p>大自然の中で美しく響くストリングスとピアノがたまらなく切ない音楽です。恋人と過ごしながらまったりと過ごしてみてはいかがでしょうか。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0023P809S?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0023P809S" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Autumn Never Fall-Sunwrae']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fautumn-never-fall%252Fid311886433%253Fi%253D311886434%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTIS" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Autumn Never Fall-Sunwrae']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/through-friendly-waters.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/through.jpg" alt="Through Friendly Waters / Kettel" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/through-friendly-waters.php">Through Friendly Waters<br />Kettel</a></h4><p>何人かで楽しく過ごしているときにかけたくなる音楽です。陽気なノリにタイトでキレのいいビートが会話の中に溶け込んでしまいそうです。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000N0WWNU?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000N0WWNU" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Through Friendly Waters-Kettel']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fthrough-friendly-waters%252Fid101706993%253Fi%253D101706784%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Through Friendly Waters-Kettel']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/raw-cuts-vol-1.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/motorcity.jpg" alt="Raw Cuts, Vol. 1 / Motor City Drum Ensemble" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/raw-cuts-vol-1.php">Raw Cuts, Vol. 1<br />Motor City Drum Ensemble</a></h4><p>海などで大音量でかけてみてはいかがでしょう。とても心地よいトラックのハウス/エレクトロニカ音楽。周囲の迷惑にならない程度にできるだけ大きな音で聴きましょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002X66RWO?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002X66RWO" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Raw Cuts, Vol. 1-Motor City Drum Ensemble']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fraw-cuts-3%252Fid347002021%253Fi%253D347002047%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTISTNAME: " onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Raw Cuts, Vol. 1-Motor City Drum Ensemble']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/the-fabric.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/thefabric.jpg" alt="The Fabric / Post-Foetus" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/the-fabric.php">The Fabric<br />Post-Foetus</a></h4><p>ポップで心地よいサウンドのエレクトロニカ。情景が浮かぶような音楽です。何度もリピートしてかけても全く気にならないでしょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0035ZFBFQ?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0035ZFBFQ" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'The Fabric-Post-Foetus']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fkiki%252Fid351542947%253Fi%253D351542966%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTISTNAME: Post-F" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'The Fabric-Post-Foetus']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/wind-mill.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/windmill.jpg" alt="Wind Mill / Naph" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/wind-mill.php">Wind Mill<br />Naph</a></h4><p>日本人アーティストによるアンビエント/ギター演奏の作品。この音楽が似合う場所は間違いなく「海」ででょう。夜空や夕焼けを見ながら黄昏れたくなります。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003DMTHWY?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003DMTHWY" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Wind Mill-Naph']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fspring-bridge%252Fid370130627%253Fi%253D370130648%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTISTNAM" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Wind Mill-Naph']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/fahrenheit-fair-enough.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/fahrenheitfairenough.jpg" alt="Fahrenheit Fair Enough / Telefon Tel Aviv" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/fahrenheit-fair-enough.php">Fahrenheit Fair Enough<br />Telefon Tel Aviv</a></h4><p>海でも山でもといったオールラウンドで活躍しそうな本作品はスタンダードなエレクトロニカ。心地よく響くシンセがビートとミックスされていて気持ちがとても盛り上がります。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00005RTBV?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00005RTBV" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Fahrenheit Fair Enough-Telefon Tel Aviv']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Ffahrenheit-fair-enough%252Fid4506184%253Fi%253D4506164%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTI" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Fahrenheit Fair Enough-Telefon Tel Aviv']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/sum-of-an-abstract.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/sumofanabstract.jpg" alt="Sum of an Abstract / Run Return" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/sum-of-an-abstract.php">Sum of an Abstract<br />Run Return</a></h4><p>生楽器中心のポストロックサウンド。山で是非聴いてみてください。電子音と生楽器の融合がたまらなく美しい作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000P1KP0O?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000P1KP0O" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Sum of an Abstract-Run Return']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fi